com.riverbed.jsconapi.rest

Class SconSiteAPI

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.riverbed.jsconapi.rest.SconSiteAPI
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SconObjectAPI

    public class SconSiteAPI
extends java.lang.Object
implements SconObjectAPI
    This class provides the primitives to create, update, get or delete Sites on SteelConnect. It will make the appropriate REST API calls to a given SCM organization.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    rjourdan rjourdan@riverbed.com
